    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-1a' );" name="009-1a" class="pb">[009-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　三家詩拾遺卷九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:221'>　　　　　　　　　　柳州府知府范家相撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='221:226'>　大雅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='226:230'>文王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='230:253'>　齊詩翼奉曰周公作詩深戒成王以恐失天下書則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='253:274'>　曰母若殷王受詩則曰殷之未䘮師克配上帝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='274:297'>　　按吕氏春秋引首二句亦云周公作詩以繩成王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='297:323'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-1b' );" name="009-1b" class="pb">[009-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='323:346'>　　之德三家之說皆同毛序云受命作周未嘗言其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='346:369'>　　帝制為天子也自緯書有改正易朔之說康成據</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='369:388'>　　之以說經所以不免為王肅之深譏也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='388:406'>殷士膚敏祼将于京厥作祼将常服黼冔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='406:429'>　魯詩劉向曰孔子論詩至於殷士膚敏祼将于京喟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='429:452'>　然嘆曰大哉天命善不可以不傳於子孫是以富貴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='452:475'>　無常不如是則王公何以戒慎民萌何以勸勉蓋傷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='475:489'>　㣲子之事周而痛殷之亡也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='489:515'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-2a' );" name="009-2a" class="pb">[009-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='515:525'>無念爾祖聿修厥德</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='525:548'>　齊詩匡衡曰無念爾祖聿修厥德孔子著之孝經之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='548:559'>　首章貴至德之本也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='559:576'>無遏爾躬　韓傳遏病也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='576:580'>大明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='580:596'>昭事上帝聿<span class='krp-note'>古作/允</span>懷多福</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='596:619'>　董仲舒曰昭事上帝允懷多福多福者非謂人也事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='619:630'>　功也謂天之所福也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='630:656'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-2b' );" name="009-2b" class="pb">[009-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='656:682'>俔天之妹　韓傳俔作磬譬也<span class='krp-note'>釋文喻說/文譬  也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='682:692'>上帝臨女無貳爾心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='692:715'>　董仲舒曰人孰無善善不一不足以立身治孰無常</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='715:738'>　常不一不足以立功詩曰上帝臨女無貳爾心知天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='738:745'>　道之常也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='745:765'>維師尚父時維鷹揚凉<span class='krp-note'>韓作/亮</span>彼武王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='765:789'>　魯詩劉向曰師之尚之父之故曰師尚父<span class='krp-note'>别/録</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='789:816'>　韓傳亮相也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>　按爾雅釋詁云亮者介尚右也左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='816:842'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-3a' );" name="009-3a" class="pb">[009-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='842:854'>　　右亮也轉以亮為訓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='854:857'>緜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='857:888'>緜緜𤓰瓞　自土<span class='krp-note'>齊作/杜</span>沮漆　韓傳瓞小𤓰也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='888:911'>　齊詩顔師古曰齊詩自杜沮漆言公劉遷狄而來居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='911:928'>　杜與沮漆之地<span class='krp-note'>漢地理/志注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='928:943'>周原膴膴　捄之陾陾度之薨薨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='943:960'>　韓傳膴膴美也度填也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='960:983'>　　說文捄盛土於虆也陾陾築墻聲則度是填土於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='983:1009'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-3b' );" name="009-3b" class="pb">[009-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1009:1028'>　　墻之意毛訓度為居非也薨薨人衆聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1028:1047'>臯門有伉　韓傳伉作閌盛也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1047:1051'>棫樸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1051:1074'>　賈誼容經曰君子重襲小人無由入正人十倍邪僻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1074:1097'>　無由來古之人其謹於所近乎詩曰濟濟辟王左右</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1097:1120'>　趨之此言左右日以善趨也　王厚齋曰此即選左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1120:1143'>　右之說　董仲舒曰文王受天命以王天下先郊乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1143:1166'>　敢行事而興師代崇其詩曰奉璋峩峩髦士攸宜此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1166:1192'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-4a' );" name="009-4a" class="pb">[009-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1192:1215'>　郊詞也其下曰周王于邁六師及之此伐詞也其下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1215:1238'>　曰文王受命有此武功既伐于崇作邑于豐以此詞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1238:1253'>　者知文王受命則郊郊乃伐崇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1253:1276'>　　鄭箋大意略同蓋魯詩說也按王制天子将出類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1276:1299'>　　乎上帝宜乎社造乎禰諸侯将出宜乎社造乎禰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1299:1322'>　　文為方伯興師伐崇宜行諸侯宜社之禮而詩云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1322:1345'>　　爾者受殷王之命而專征郊亦殷王之命也周公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1345:1368'>　　作此追崇功徳故以追王之禮稱王蓋受王命行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1368:1394'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-4b' );" name="009-4b" class="pb">[009-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1394:1417'>　　郊即受天命耳江都以文王王天下而自行帝制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1417:1440'>　　行郊非是但詩先言左右奉璋後言六師及之是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1440:1451'>　　先郊後伐甚明也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1451:1462'>左右奉璋　六師及之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1462:1485'>　董仲舒曰左右奉璋此文王之郊也六師及之言文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1485:1513'>　王之伐崇也<span class='krp-note'>春秋/繁露</span>　班固曰六師及之言五人為伍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1513:1536'>　五伍為兩四兩為卒五卒為旅五旅為師師二千五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1536:1557'>　百人為一軍六師萬五千人也<span class='krp-note'>白虎/通</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1557:1583'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-5a' );" name="009-5a" class="pb">[009-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1583:1606'>追琢其章金玉其相　魯詩言其質美也<span class='krp-note'>說/苑</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1606:1610'>旱麓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1610:1628'>瞻彼旱麓榛楛濟濟豈弟君子干禄豈弟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1628:1651'>　韋昭曰王者之德被及榛楛隂陽調草木盛故君子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1651:1668'>　以求禄其心豈弟矣<span class='krp-note'>國語/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1668:1691'>　　國語夫旱鹿之榛楛殖故君子得以易樂干禄若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1691:1714'>　　夫山林匱竭林鹿散亡藪澤肆既民力彫盡田疇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1714:1737'>　　荒蕪資用之匱君子将險哀之不暇而何樂易之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1737:1763'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-5b' );" name="009-5b" class="pb">[009-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1763:1786'>　　有此釋詩意甚明韋昭之注不必盡出三家附而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1786:1799'>　　録之見古義之可從耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1799:1809'>鳶飛戾天魚躍于淵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1809:1832'>　韓詩薛君曰魚喜樂則踴躍於淵中<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1832:1855'>　　薛君之意蓋以鳶魚喻干禄之君子以戾天躍淵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1855:1878'>　　喻其干禄之豈弟故曰喜樂而躍淵以興文王作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1878:1897'>　　人之雅化與中庸斷章引詩之意不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1897:1923'>清酒旣載騂牡旣備　韓詩薛君曰載設也<span class='krp-note'>後漢/書注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1923:1949'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-6a' );" name="009-6a" class="pb">[009-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1949:1953'>思齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1953:1965'>思媚周姜　太姒嗣徽音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1965:1988'>　魯詩劉向曰太姒號曰文母思媚太姜旦夕勤勞以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1988:2012'>　盡婦道文王理外太姒理内生十子也<span class='krp-note'>列/傳</span>女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2012:2039'>肆成人有德小子有造　魯詩劉向曰大學之教也<span class='krp-note'>説/苑</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2039:2059'>皇矣　齊詩匡衡曰言天以文王之居為都也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2059:2075'>作之屛之其葘其翳<span class='krp-note'>韓作/殪</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2075:2101'>　韓詩薛君曰葘反草也殪因也因高填下也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2101:2127'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-6b' );" name="009-6b" class="pb">[009-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2127:2145'>惟此王季因心則友則友其兄則篤其慶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2145:2168'>　韓外傳太伯知太王賢昌欲季為後也去之吳太王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2168:2191'>　将死謂季歴曰女往讓兩兄有義而安太王薨季之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2191:2214'>　呉告伯仲伯仲從季而歸羣臣欲伯之立季季又讓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2214:2237'>　伯伯謂仲曰何以處之仲曰刑有所謂矣要於挾微</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2237:2245'>　者可以立季</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2245:2270'>　　太王既死王季不顧宗社被喪服逺而之吳非理也羣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2270:2293'>　　臣既欲立季而伯復商之於仲似存繋戀尤非理</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2293:2319'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-7a' );" name="009-7a" class="pb">[009-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2319:2340'>維此王季<span class='krp-note'>韓作文王/與左傳同</span>貊其徳音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2340:2367'>　韓傳貊作莫定也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>　此章韓詩與左傳俱作文王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2367:2390'>　　王肅注亦同按上章受禄無䘮奄有四方既指文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2390:2413'>　　王則此章亦指文王為是即毛傳克順克比亦全</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2413:2436'>　　據左傳為說是毛詩本作文王可見矣孔氏頴達</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2436:2451'>　　曰經涉亂離故師有異讀耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2451:2471'>無然畔援無然歆羨　侵阮徂共　以遏徂莒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2471:2489'>　韓詩畔援武強也羨願也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2489:2515'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-7b' );" name="009-7b" class="pb">[009-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2515:2538'>　魯詩鄭氏曰阮徂共三國犯周文王伐之密須之人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2538:2559'>　乃敢拒其義兵爰整其軍旅以却止徂國之兵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2559:2578'>　張融曰魯詩以阮徂共皆國名與毛不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2578:2600'>無矢我陵　韓詩薛君曰四平曰陵<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2600:2610'>不識不知順帝之則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2610:2633'>　賈誼曰弗識弗知順帝之則言民悅其徳義則傚而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2633:2660'>　象之也<span class='krp-note'>新/書</span>　董仲舒曰言弗能知識而效天之所為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2660:2672'>　云爾<span class='krp-note'>春秋/繁露</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2672:2698'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-8a' );" name="009-8a" class="pb">[009-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2698:2721'>　　按不識二句康衢之謡有之賈生之言似本古說</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2721:2743'>詢爾仇方同爾兄弟以爾鉤援與爾臨衝以伐崇墉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2743:2772'>　齊詩伏湛曰<span class='krp-note'>湛從匡衡/受齊詩</span>文王受命征伐五國必先詢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2772:2795'>　之同姓然後謀之羣臣加占蓍蔡以定行事故謀則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2795:2818'>　成卜則吉詩云云崇固城守先退後伐所以重人命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2818:2838'>　俟時而動故三分天下有其二<span class='krp-note'>漢/書</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2838:2856'>崇墉仡仡　韓詩仡仡摇也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2856:2860'>靈臺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2860:2886'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-8b' );" name="009-8b" class="pb">[009-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2886:2909'>　魯詩劉向曰積恩為愛積愛為仁積仁為靈靈臺之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2909:2932'>　所以為靈者積仁也神靈者天地之本萬物之始也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2932:2940'>　<span class='krp-note'>説/苑</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2940:2964'>　班固曰天子之所以有靈臺者何所以考天人之心察</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2964:2991'>　隂陽之㑹揆星辰之證騐為萬物獲福無方之元<span class='krp-note'>白/虎</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2991:2998'>　<span class='krp-note'>通/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2998:3008'>庶民攻之不日成之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3008:3031'>　賈誼曰文王有志為臺令近規之民聞之者麇裹而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3031:3057'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-9a' );" name="009-9a" class="pb">[009-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3057:3080'>　至問業而作之日日以衆故勿趨以疾<span class='krp-note'>新/書</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3080:3103'>　　孔叢子云文王之興六州之衆各以子來故區區</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3103:3126'>　　之臺未及期日而成蓋不日成之非如集傳所云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3126:3140'>　　不終日而成也賈說正同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3140:3151'>王在靈囿　王在靈沼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3151:3174'>　賈誼曰文王之澤下被禽獸洽於魚鼈咸若攸樂而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3174:3185'>　况人乎<span class='krp-note'>新/書</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3185:3211'>　韓詩薛君曰文王聖德上及飛鳥下及魚鼈<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3211:3237'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-9b' );" name="009-9b" class="pb">[009-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3237:3247'>於論鼔鐘於樂辟雍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3247:3270'>　韓傳辟雍者天子之學圓如璧壅之以水示圓也言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3270:3293'>　璧者取辟有徳之義不言辟水言辟雍者取其雝和</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3293:3316'>　也所以教天下春射秋饗尊事三老五更在南方七</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3316:3343'>　里之内五經之文所藏處蓋以茅葦取其潔清也<span class='krp-note'>正/義</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3343:3370'>　<span class='krp-note'>公羊/疏</span>　又春旱使人禱於山川君親之南郊以六事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3370:3393'>　自責曰政不一歟民失職歟宫室崇歟苞苴行歟讒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3393:3422'>　夫倡歟婦謁盛歟<span class='krp-note'>公羊疏/引内傳</span>　班固曰天子立辟雍何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3422:3449'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-10a' );" name="009-10a" class="pb">[009-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3449:3470'>　所以行禮樂宣徳化也辟者璧也象璧圓又以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3470:3493'>　法天於雍水象教化之流行也辟之為言積也積天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3493:3514'>　下之道徳也雍之為言壅也壅天下之殘賊也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3514:3536'>文王有聲　文王烝哉　韓詩烝美也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3536:3563'>築城伊淢　王公伊濯　韓詩淢作洫深也濯美也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3563:3573'>貽厥孫謀以燕翼子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3573:3596'>　魯詩晏安也翼敬也言文王貽其孫以善謀以安敬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3596:3616'>　之道貽其子子謂武王也<span class='krp-note'>班彪/傳注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3616:3643'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-10b' );" name="009-10b" class="pb">[009-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3643:3647'>生民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3647:3670'>履帝武敏歆攸介攸止載震載夙載生載育時維后稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3670:3693'>　魯詩司馬遷曰姜原為帝嚳元妃出野見巨人跡心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3693:3716'>　欣悅欲踐之踐之而心動如孕者居期而生子　劉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3716:3739'>　向曰姜嫄行見巨人跡好而履之歸而有娠卜筮禋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3739:3766'>　祀以求無子終生子以為不祥而棄之<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span>　鄭氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3766:3789'>　曰帝上帝敏拇也介左右也夙之言肅也祀郊禖之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3789:3812'>　時時則有大神之跡姜嫄履之足不能滿履其拇指</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3812:3839'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-11a' );" name="009-11a" class="pb">[009-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3839:3862'>　之處心體歆歆其左右所止住如有人道感己者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3862:3888'>　遂有娠而肅戒不復御生子而養長名曰棄<span class='krp-note'>毛詩/箋</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3888:3912'>　　按鄭異義云詩魯齊韓春秋公羊說皆無父感天而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3912:3935'>　　生故與毛傳不同蓋鄭信緯書故不主毛傳也朱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3935:3954'>　　子亦遵鄭說宋惟蘓老泉與鄭異而已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3954:3980'>　<span class='krp-note'>附/</span>河圖曰姜嫄履大人跡生后稷　中候稷起曰耀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3980:4003'>　　倉稷生感跡　昌契握云元鳥翔水遺卵流娀簡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4003:4021'>　　吞之生契封商興曰契卵生稷迹乳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4021:4048'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-11b' );" name="009-11b" class="pb">[009-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4048:4071'>誕寘之隘巷牛羊腓字之誕寘之平林㑹伐平林誕寘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4071:4095'>之寒冰鳥覆翼之鳥乃去矣后稷<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0561' title='KR0561' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0561.png'/>矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4095:4118'>　魯詩司馬遷曰姜原以棄為不祥棄之隘巷馬牛過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4118:4141'>　者皆辟不踐從置之林中㑹山林多人遷而棄渠中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4141:4164'>　之冰上飛鳥以其翼覆薦之姜原以為神遂收養之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4164:4187'>　褚少孫曰后稷母姜嫄出見巨人跡而履踐之知於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4187:4210'>　身則生稷姜嫄以為無父賤而棄之牛羊避不踐抱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4210:4233'>　之山中山者養之又捐之大澤鳥覆席食之姜嫄怪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4233:4260'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-12a' );" name="009-12a" class="pb">[009-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4260:4283'>　之乃取長之堯知其賢立以為大農姓之曰姬氏姬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4283:4306'>　者大也詩人美而頌之曰厥初生民深修益成而道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4306:4329'>　后稷之始也<span class='krp-note'>史記三代世表/褚先生述詩傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4329:4356'>茀<span class='krp-note'>韓作/拂</span>厥豐草　韓詩薛君曰拂弗也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4356:4381'>鳬鷖　鳬鷖在亹　韓詩薛君曰亹水流也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4381:4385'>假樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4385:4402'>顯顯<span class='krp-note'>中庸/作憲</span>令德保佑命之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4402:4431'>　鄭氏中庸注憲憲興盛之貌保安也佑助也<span class='krp-note'>正義曰/此齊魯</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4431:4458'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-12b' );" name="009-12b" class="pb">[009-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4458:4466'>　<span class='krp-note'>韓/詩</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4466:4469'>板</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4469:4480'>䘮亂蔑資曽莫惠我師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4480:4504'>　魯詩劉向曰此傷奢侈不節以為亂者也<span class='krp-note'>說/苑</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4504:4510'>牖民孔易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4510:4533'>　韓外傳聖王之教民也必因其情而節之以禮必從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4533:4556'>　其欲而制之以義義簡而備禮易而法故民之從命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4556:4564'>　也速詩云云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4564:4591'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-13a' );" name="009-13a" class="pb">[009-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4591:4594'>蕩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4594:4612'>天生蒸民其命匪諶靡不有初鮮克有終</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4612:4635'>　韓外傳夫人性善非得聖帝明王扶携之以道則不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4635:4644'>　成君子詩云云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4644:4664'>不明爾徳時無背無側爾徳不明以無陪無卿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4664:4687'>　韓外傳同明相見同音相聞同志相從非賢者莫能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4687:4695'>　用賢詩云云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4695:4717'>　　毛傳背無人側無人無陪貳無卿士義與韓同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4717:4744'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-13b' );" name="009-13b" class="pb">[009-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4744:4769'>天不湎爾以酒　韓傳飲酒閉門不出客曰湎<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4769:4772'>抑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4772:4795'>　韓詩侯包曰衞武公刺王室亦以自戒行年九十五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4795:4820'>　猶使人日誦是詩而不離於其側<span class='krp-note'>侯包傳/韓詩學</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4820:4831'>　　事詳國語抑作懿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4831:4841'>有覺徳行四國順之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4841:4864'>　董仲舒曰覺者著也王者有明著之徳行則四方莫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4864:4883'>　不響應風化善於彼矣<span class='krp-note'>春秋/繁露</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4883:4910'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-14a' );" name="009-14a" class="pb">[009-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4910:4933'>　　覺毛訓為直鄭改為大以禮記引此二句以有覺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4933:4956'>　　作有牿耳似江都義長韓詩外傳亦云貴名自揚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4956:4962'>　　天下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4962:4982'>曰䘮厥國　韓詩曰作聿語辭也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4982:5002'>桑柔　征以中垢　韓外傳征以中垢闇行也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='5002:5006'>雲漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='5006:5029'>　董仲舒曰宣王之時天下大旱歲惡甚王憂之其詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='5029:5048'>　曰倬彼雲漢為章于天<span class='krp-note'>春秋/繁露</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5048:5075'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-14b' );" name="009-14b" class="pb">[009-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5075:5087'>倬<span class='krp-note'>韓作/對</span>彼雲漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5087:5113'>　韓詩對彼雲漢宣王遭旱仰天也<span class='krp-note'>薛君章句/文選注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5113:5141'>藴隆蟲蟲<span class='krp-note'>韓作鬰/隆烱烱</span>　后稷不克上帝不臨耗斁下土</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5141:5164'>　董仲舒曰宣王自以為不能乎后稷不中乎上帝故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5164:5184'>　有此灾愈恐懼而謹事天<span class='krp-note'>春秋/繁露</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5184:5201'>　韓詩鬰隆為暑耗惡也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5201:5224'>我心憚暑　胡寜瘨我以旱　韓傳憚苦瘨作疹重也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5224:5232'>　<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5232:5259'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-15a' );" name="009-15a" class="pb">[009-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5259:5263'>崧高</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5263:5273'>維嶽降神生甫及申</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5273:5296'>　韓詩鄭氏曰周道将興五嶽為之生賢輔佐仲山甫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5296:5313'>　及申伯為周之幹臣<span class='krp-note'>禮記/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5313:5336'>　　孔頴達曰鄭注禮記未見毛序故以申甫為仲山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5336:5358'>　　甫按鄭所主乃韓詩之說觀下所載外傳可見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5358:5368'>周邦咸喜戎有良翰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5368:5391'>　韓外傳周徳大壞廢於厲王仲山甫輔相宣王撥亂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5391:5418'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-15b' );" name="009-15b" class="pb">[009-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5418:5441'>　反正並順天下匡救邪失喻徳教舉遺士天下翕然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5441:5454'>　向風咏宣王之徳詩云云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5454:5458'>烝民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5458:5481'>民之秉彛好是懿德　韓外傳民之秉徳所以則天也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5481:5491'>柔亦不茹剛亦不吐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5491:5514'>　韓外傳君子崇人之徳揚人之善非道諛也正言直</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5514:5537'>　行指人之過非指毁也詘柔順從剛強與物周流道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5537:5543'>　徳不外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5543:5570'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-16a' );" name="009-16a" class="pb">[009-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5570:5581'>德輶如毛民鮮克舉之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5581:5603'>　董仲舒曰德輶如毛言其易也<span class='krp-note'>春秋/繁露</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5603:5626'>　韓外傳至精而妙乎天地之間者徳也微聖人其孰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5626:5633'>　能與於此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5633:5656'>　　按荀子曰能積微者逺成詩曰德輶如毛民鮮克</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='5656:5673'>　　舉之積微者積細微以成全德也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='5673:5684'>仲山甫徂齊式遄其歸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='5684:5707'>　韓詩杜欽曰仲山甫異姓之臣無親於宣就封於齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='5707:5734'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-16b' );" name="009-16b" class="pb">[009-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='5734:5754'>　<span class='krp-note'>漢書/本傳</span>鄧展注韓詩以為封於齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='5754:5777'>　　按齊為太公封國未見宣王時復封於齊毛傳亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='5777:5789'>　　同孔疏云不知所出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='5789:5793'>韓奕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='5793:5804'>有倬其道　幹不庭方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='5804:5831'>　韓傳倬作晫明也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>　薛君曰幹正也謂以其義非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='5831:5843'>　而正之<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='5843:5847'>江漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5847:5874'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-17a' );" name="009-17a" class="pb">[009-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5874:5889'>無曰予小子召公是似肇敏戎公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5889:5912'>　韓外傳予小子使爾繼召公之後受命者必以其祖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='5912:5928'>　命之　内傳肇長也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='5928:5946'>釐爾圭瓚秬鬯一卣告爾文人錫山土田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='5946:5969'>　韓外傳諸侯之有徳天子錫之一錫車馬再錫衣服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='5969:5992'>　三錫虎賁四錫樂器五錫納陛六錫朱户七錫弓矢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='5992:6003'>　八錫圭瓚九錫秬鬯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='6003:6007'>常武</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='6007:6034'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-17b' );" name="009-17b" class="pb">[009-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='6034:6044'>王命卿士南仲太祖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='6044:6067'>　班固曰王制爵人於朝與衆共之詩云云祭統曰古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6067:6086'>　者人君爵有徳必於太祖<span class='krp-note'>白虎/通</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='6086:6109'>　　按毛傳王命南仲於太祖皇父為太師而鄭箋改</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='6109:6132'>　　之曰宣王命卿士為大將用其以南仲為太祖者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='6132:6155'>　　今之太師皇父是也蓋以南仲為文王時人今所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='6155:6178'>　　命者皇父是其後人也孫毓云古之命將皆於禰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='6178:6201'>　　廟未有於后稷之廟又經言南仲太祖明以南仲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='6201:6228'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '009-18a' );" name="009-18a" class="pb">[009-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='6228:6251'>　　為太祖也箋義為長按南仲太祖自當如鄭箋以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='6251:6274'>　　南仲為太祖者今之太師為是但遣將如祭統所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='6274:6294'>　　言未嘗不可在太祖之廟也亦不可不知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='6294:6316'>鋪敦淮濆　韓傳鋪作敷大也敦迫也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='6316:6319'>　</span><br/>
